I"£<ol>
  <li>
    <p>You learn to connect with your different and contradictory ways of acting in the world. This raises your awareness of your behaviour and helps you to make sense of how you can seem to be different versions of yourself in different circumstances.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>You learn to free yourself of the unconscious forces that cause you to get trapped in certain aspects of your personality. 
For example, a very critical part of yourself.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>You integrate the different aspects of your personality which causes you to feel less conflict within yourself.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>You emphasise all of the beneficial qualities of your sub-personalities and recognise how they serve you.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>By identifying with your different sub-peronalities, it allows you to develop a greater awareness of what is your true self and what is a mask or persona.</p>
  </li>
</ol>
